soot.toolkits.graph

Class DominatorTreeAdapter<N>

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.toolkits.graph.DominatorTreeAdapter<N>
  • Type Parameters:
    N -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<DominatorNode<N>>, DirectedGraph<DominatorNode<N>>

    public class DominatorTreeAdapter<N>
extends Object
implements DirectedGraph<DominatorNode<N>>
    This adapter provides a DirectedGraph interface to DominatorTree.

    This might be useful if e.g. you want to apply a DirectedGraph analysis such as the PseudoTopologicalOrderer to a DominatorTree.

    Author:
    Navindra Umanee
